<body class="landing">
	<div id="page-wrapper">

		<!-- Header -->
			<header id="header" class="alt">
				<h1><a href="index.html">Racing+</a></h1>
				<nav id="nav">
					<ul>
						<li><a href="/news">News</a></li>
						<li><a href="/races">Race Listing</a></li>
						<li><a href="/profiles">Player Profiles</a></li>
						<li><a href="/leaderboards">Leaderboard</a></li>
						<li><a href="/help">Help</a></li>
						<li><a href="/download" class="button special">Download</a></li>
					</ul>
				</nav>
			</header>

		<!-- Banner -->
			<section id="banner">

				<h2>
					<span style="position: relative; right: 10px; top: 20px;"><img src="/public/img/The_Belt_Icon.png" class="belt"></span>
					Racing+
				</h2>
				<p>A racing mod for The Binding of Isaac: Afterbirth+.</p>
				<ul class="actions">
					<li><a href="/download" class="button special">Download</a></li>
					<li><a href="#" id="learn-more" class="button">Learn More</a></li>
				</ul>
			</section>

		<!-- Main -->
			<span id="scroll-to-here"></span>
			<section id="main" class="container">

				<section class="box special">
					<header class="major">
						<h2>Race other Isaac players head to head.</h2>
						<p>It's free, and it couldn't be easier. Race your friends or make new ones.</p>
					</header>
				</section>

				<section class="box special features">
					<div class="features-row">
						<section>
							<span class="icon major fa-flag-checkered accent2"></span>
							<h3>Integrated Racing</h3>
							<p>Everything is integrated within the game. You can play a 1v1 or race a bunch of people at the same time. Streaming isn't required.</p>
						</section>
						<section>
							<span class="icon major fa-area-chart accent3"></span>
							<h3>Statistics & Leaderboards</h3>
							<p>The server will keep track of all of your races and times. Compete with others to get the lowest average time. Unlike the vanilla leaderboards, cheaters will be banned.</p>
						</section>
					</div>
					<div class="features-row">
						<section>
							<span class="icon major accent4 fa-stack">
								<strong class="fa-stack-2x" style="color: white;">1P</strong>
							</span>
							<h3>Single-Player & Practice</h3>
							<p>If no-one else is around, you can always start a race by yourself. Or, if you need to get better at using a specific item, use the practice mode to start a run with that item.</p>
						</section>
						<section>
							<span class="icon major fa-bug accent5"></span>
							<h3>Bug Fixes</h3>
							<p>Enjoy an updated client that includes hundreds of bug fixes that remain unpatched in the vanilla game.</p>
						</section>
					</div>
					<div class="features-row">
						<section>
							<span class="icon major fa-trophy accent6"></span>
							<h3>Achievements</h3>
							<p>Why not? With over 100 optional achievements, there's plenty to do.</p>
						</section>
						<section>
							<span class="icon major fa-wrench accent7"></span>
							<h3>Continuous Improvement</h3>
							<p>We want the client and the platform to be the best it can possibly be. The Racing+ team will work with the community to iron out all of the bugs and implement the best suggestions.</p>
						</section>
					</div>
				</section>

			</section>

	</div>
